'''Razmire Keelgan''' is located at [[Mort'ton]] and runs both the [[Razmire General Store|general store]] and the [[Razmire Builders Merchants|building supplies]]. He is afflicted at first, but he can be cured either by using [[Serum 207]] (temporarily) or [[Serum 208]] (permanently) on him. He also plays a role in the [[Shades of Mort'ton]] [[quest]].

